Kapetane!

17
00:01:18,480 --> 00:01:20,516
Nešto je iznad oblaka!

18
00:01:23,440 --> 00:01:24,475
Gde?

19
00:01:27,320 --> 00:01:28,389
Šta je to?

20
00:01:55,400 --> 00:01:57,311
Eno ga još jedan!

21
